# Environment Variables for XPS Intelligence Control Plane

# ===== REQUIRED =====

# Supabase Configuration (for control plane database & vault)
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# Groq LLM API (for AI chat functionality)
AI_GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# ===== OPTIONAL (for integration testing) =====

# GitHub Integration
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...

# Vercel Integration
VERCEL_TOKEN=...

# Railway Backend
RAILWAY_TOKEN=...
BACKEND_URL=https://your-backend.railway.app

# Existing Backend API (if different from Railway)
VITE_API_URL=https://xpsintelligencesystem-production.up.railway.app/api
VITE_WS_URL=wss://xpsintelligencesystem-production.up.railway.app

# ===== NOTES =====

# 1. SUPABASE_URL and SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY are REQUIRED for the control plane to function.
#    Get these from your Supabase project settings.

# 2. AI_GROQ_API_KEY is REQUIRED for chat functionality.
#    Get this from https://console.groq.com

# 3. Integration tokens (GITHUB_TOKEN, VERCEL_TOKEN, etc.) are OPTIONAL.
#    If not set, the diagnostics page will show "not configured" status.
#    Users can also connect their own tokens via the UI (when implemented).

# 4. For production deployment to Vercel:
#    - Add these variables in Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables
#    - Mark sensitive keys (tokens, service role key) as "Encrypted"
#    - Set appropriate scopes (Production, Preview, Development)
